Patch Set 9:

On gating, I force global.repository to nexus3 repo (for "historical" reason, I could remove it).
if you look at 
{{- define "common.repository" -}}
  {{if .Values.repositoryOverride }}
    {{- printf "%s" .Values.repositoryOverride -}}
  {{else}}
    {{- default .Values.repository .Values.global.repository -}}
  {{end}}
{{- end -}}

you'll see repository value is only used if no global repository.

In constrained environment (no real access to Internet for example), I think it's preferable to have only one repository to take care so  I think that second solution is better
